source.name: Building Footprints (Zipped Shapefile Format)
source.description: This data layer shows building footprints for the City and County of San Francisco as of June 2011. The layer was created using the ArcGIS 3D Analyst conversion tool, "MultiPatch Footprint," converting the 3D building model data the City licensed from PIctometry, Inc.
